excerpt.rendered:
DESCRIPTION
Full Cheeks Timothy Hay Sticks Treats & Chews are made with love for guinea pigs, rabbits, chinchillas, and other small animals. These chew treats also satisfy your pet’s instinctive urge to chew, and offer a satisfying crunch your pet will love. We believe caring for your furry little one should be as easy as loving them, and now it can be. Our products are specially made for them, and are designed to be simple for you. All they need to do is what they do best: give lots of love. Only at PetSmart.

Features:

Helps encourage chewing behaviors
Satisfying crunch of hay
All-natural

Includes: (7) Timothy Hay Sticks Treats and Chews

Intended Pet(s): Guinea Pigs, Rabbits, Chinchillas, and other small animals

Product Weight: 0.92 oz (26 g)
